---
title: "Account"
subtitle: "Sign in and manage your preferences."
layout: layouts/page.njk
breadcrumbs:
  - label: "Home"
    href: "/"
  - label: "Account"
---

<p class="muted">
  This is a placeholder account page for the static build. If you add customer accounts later (Shopify/Stripe + auth),
  you can replace this page.
</p>

<p class="muted">
  Admins: use the <a href="/admin/">/admin/</a> page to manage products.
</p>

<div class="card" style="padding:16px; max-width:480px;">
  <h2 class="card-title">Sign in</h2>
  <form class="form" method="post" data-account-form>
    <div class="form-row">
      <label class="label" for="account-email">Email</label>
      <input class="input" id="account-email" type="email" autocomplete="email" />
    </div>
    <div class="form-row">
      <label class="label" for="account-pass">Password</label>
      <input class="input" id="account-pass" type="password" autocomplete="current-password" />
    </div>
    <button class="btn btn-primary" type="submit">Sign in</button>
    <p class="muted" style="display:none; margin-top:10px;" data-account-feedback></p>
  </form>
</div>
